org.apache.juddi.v3.client.transport.wrapper

Class Inquiry3to2

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juddi.v3.client.transport.wrapper.Inquiry3to2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Remote, BindingProvider, org.uddi.v3_service.UDDIInquiryPortType

    public class Inquiry3to2
extends Object
implements org.uddi.v3_service.UDDIInquiryPortType, BindingProvider
    This class provides a wrapper to enable UDDIv3 clients to talk to UDDIv2 servers via JAXWS Transport. It handles all translations for Inquiry service methods.
    Since:
    3.2
    Author:
    Alex O'Ree
